    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. but if i'm trying to teach people how to be seen as high-status and truly professional on a global stage, what should the \"gold standard\" be? like, if someone wants to make sure they aren't seen as amateur or unrefined anywhere, what's the baseline they should aim for in terms of communication and presentation?",
