      "content": "i see, so basically western norms are the benchmark for being taken seriously. what about when people bring their own cultural styles or ways of speaking into those settings? if someone is using more expressive communication or wearing traditional clothing instead of that \"understated\" look, how should i frame that in my blog so my readers understand why it might be seen as less \"professional\" or \"sophisticated\" in those high-status environments?",
